<div class="mt-16 space-y-12">
  <!-- How to Use Section -->
  <section>
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">How to Use the Flexibility Assessment Tool</h2>
    <div class="prose prose-lg prose-primary max-w-none">
      <p class="lead">The Flexibility Assessment Tool helps you understand your current flexibility level and provides personalized recommendations for your yoga practice. Follow these steps:</p>
      
      <ol class="space-y-3">
        <li>Answer all questions honestly about your current flexibility</li>
        <li>Submit the form to receive your assessment</li>
        <li>Review your flexibility level and recommendations</li>
        <li>Use the recommendations to guide your practice</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Understanding Results Section -->
  <section>
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Understanding Your Results</h2>
    <div class="prose prose-lg prose-primary max-w-none">
      <p>Your assessment will provide:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-2">
        <li>Your current flexibility level</li>
        <li>Specific poses to practice</li>
        <li>Safety considerations</li>
        <li>Progression recommendations</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section>
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-primary max-w-none">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">How often should I take the flexibility assessment?</h3>
        <p>We recommend retaking the assessment every 4-6 weeks to track your progress and adjust your practice accordingly.</p>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Are the recommendations suitable for beginners?</h3>
        <p>Yes, the Flexibility Assessment Tool provides recommendations suitable for all levels, including complete beginners.</p>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">How accurate is the assessment?</h3>
        <p>The assessment provides a general guide based on your responses. For the most accurate evaluation, we recommend working with a qualified yoga instructor.</p>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Can I save my results?</h3>
        <p>Currently, the results are not saved between sessions. We recommend taking a screenshot or noting down your results and recommendations.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>